<L>__{interior admiral's cabin, ark royal day}
<A>__{lord howard bent over a mass of charts with his commanders round him: hawkins, drake, frobisher and raleigh. the boom of spanish cannon shakes the air. flashes of fire light the faces of the english officers.}
<C>__{drake}
<D>__{we must attack! what choice do we have?}
<C>__{howard}
<D>__{we're decisively outgunned, drake. we are losing too many ships. we must defend the coast.}
